Amanda Holden, 51, stunned fans as she posed for a poolside picture in one of the Heart FM host's latest jaw-dropping posts shared with her 1.8 million followers. The Britain’s Got Talent star looked like a sun soaked goddess as she lay down on the edge of an infinity pool against a scenic rural backdrop. Amanda flaunted her ageless looks in a tiny bikini, prompting a barrage of compliments from fans and friends on Instagram. Swimwear designer Melissa Odabash, was one of many left stunned by Amanda’s most recent post, which showed her floating on a unicorn inflatable, as she gushed: “Teenager you hottie.”